    <keyword>protocol independent multicast join attribute</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a use of the Protocol Independent Multicast (PIM) Join Attribute as defined in RFC 5384, which enables PIM to build multicast trees through an MPLS-enabled network, even if that network's IGP does not have a route to the source of the tree. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
